要檢點D唔好做變態野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"jeng wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我鍾意家姐口口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9493e5c49b0a181103db0be9a856db4da18034","tid":960371,"uid":152123,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主小心細佬變成夏健祺！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要係Google搜尋HKU精算畢業裝cam偷拍犯夏健祺的名字！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bRayFS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bRayFS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9431344ee56470f6fd38f49131661cde2e1e1323","tid":960371,"uid":141261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"呢d真係要同佢傾"},{"pid":"be2ed5c5aceaa492446acf33804f4f82004475d6","tid":960371,"uid":34203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"教佢打丁發洩"},{"pid":"7c8bfdc5cb29f155b7a099cd6aa7c386c02187ee","tid":960371,"uid":146535,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"你好細個你阿爸已經走左<br />\n咁你細佬點嚟"},{"pid":"1d02456c0b9ade30bf62834faea81b78088c1881","tid":960371,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"臭利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb94eb3701c83781fee592689b96151653be061","tid":960371,"uid":69509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"香討copy過黎 2015年post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60de139de49d9ba646cae33d7910e19240350eb7","tid":960371,"uid":59116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7c8bfdc5cb29f155b7a099c